(586, 1, '2017-06-23 16:56:46', '2017-06-23 16:56:46', '<h3>Hey people!</h3>\r\nHere are the answers to some questions customers usually has been asking us about our products.\r\n\r\n[skin-wave-divider position="horizontal" align="left" color="#353535" animate="true"/]\r\n<h4>Q1: Can I change colors on Skin?</h4>\r\nA1: Absolutely! You can change gradient colors, make one solid color, change background colors, text and link colors etc. We made it quite user friendly and easily editable through Customizer.\r\n<h4> Q2: Can I change fonts?</h4>\r\nA2: Skin comes with integrated Google fonts, so you have over 800 fonts to choose from for every group of elements on Skin (headings, paragraphs etc.)\r\n<h4> Q3: Is it possible to easily translate Skin to some other language?</h4>\r\nA3: Skin comes as a translation ready theme (for PoEdit) and you shouldn''t have any problems translating it.\r\n<h4> Q4: Is demo content included in the package?</h4>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">A4: Yes! And documentation explains how to import it easily.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Q5: Does SKIN comes with detail documentation?</h4>\r\nA5: Skin comes with step-by-step user guide on how to set up a theme with a lot print screens following the instructions.\r\n<h4> Q6: If I buy a theme, and I have problems setting it up, what should I do?</h4>\r\nA6: If you have any troubles setting up Skin, you can write to our support team at  and we will be glad to help.  And our support team is known to be very friendly and responsive. Here''s what our customers say about our support:\r\n\r\n\r\n<h4> Q7: Is your demo completely made using just SKIN theme?</h4>\r\nA7: Yes! Absolutely everything is made using only Skin theme.\r\n\r\n', 'FAQ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'faq', '', '', '2018-05-26 07:45:18', '2018-05-26 07:45:18', '', 0, 'http://skin.nordwoodthemes.com/?page_id=586', 4, 'page', '', 0),
