(721, 1, '2017-07-25 09:35:03', '2017-07-25 09:35:03', '<h3>Easily communicate with your customers using contact form</h3>\r\nThis is an example of a contact page made using free WordPress plugin: Contact Form 7.  Beside the form, you can use Google map short code we added directly to editor if you want to show your location.\r\n\r\nWe are currently located here:\r\n\r\n<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d448183.73912804417!2d76.8130664011526!3d28.646677246352574!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x390cfd5b347eb62d%3A0x37205b715389640!2sDelhi!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sin!4v1527319764830" width="800" height="400" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>\r\n<h3>Send us a mail and we''ll answer ASAP</h3>\r\nOur agency is open from 9am-5pm working days and we are usually out of the office during the weekends. Expect to hear from us during the working hours. Cheers!\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id="4" title="Contact form 1"]\r\n<h3>Don''t be a stranger!</h3>\r\nIf you want to follow our work and have more regular updates, please make sure you follow us on some social network, so you never miss an important promotion or new product release. Let stay connected!\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[skin-social-profiles align="center"/]', 'Contact us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'contact-page', '', '', '2018-05-26 07:36:55', '2018-05-26 07:36:55', '', 0, 'http://skin.nordwoodthemes.com/?page_id=721', 2, 'page', '', 0),
