uploads/2017/06/testemonial3.jpg" alt="" width="518" height="150" /><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-707" src="http://skin.nordwoodthemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/test1.jpg" alt="" width="518" height="88" /></p>\r\n<h4> Q7: Is your demo completely made using just SKIN theme?</h4>\r\n<p>A7: Yes! Absolutely everything is made using only Skin theme. </p>\r\n<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-594 size-large" src="http://skin.nordwoodthemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/questions-1024x564.jpg" alt="" width="1024" height="564" /></p>', 'FAQ', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '586-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-24 16:22:23', '2018-05-24 16:22:23', '', 586, 'http://itsugestion.com/dev/testkd/586-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
