(894, 1, '2018-05-24 17:40:39', '2018-05-24 17:40:39', 'Hello beautiful people, welcome to our sweet new WordPress blog theme, Skin. This is an example of a gallery single post. It can be without a sidebar, with a sidebar, with wide embedded media or narrow embeds. Read on.\r\n<blockquote>Hey there, this is an example of a blockquote in the Skin WordPress theme.</blockquote>\r\nYou can embed all popular social platforms like Facebook, Instagram, Twitter, Tumblr, Pinterest posts and all popular streaming media services like Soundcloud, YouTube, Vimeo, Mixcloud and much more.\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ekZEVeXwek\r\n<h4>Check out our Social media templates on Creative Market</h4>\r\nWe also create awesome Photoshop templates for social media platforms which you can buy on our Creative Market shop. Click on the button below to visit it. You can use a button like this wherever you want in the editor as a shortcode,.\r\n\r\n[skin-link-button text="Our Creative Market Shop" url="https://creativemarket.com/NordWood?u=NordWood"/]\r\n\r\n<a href="https://crmrkt.com/NjdXgp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="alignnone wp-image-473 size-full" src="http://skin.nordwoodthemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/colorful.jpg" alt="" width="590" height="393" /></a>\r\n<h4>Skin short codes: Related posts</h4>\r\nThis is a new shortcode we developed for Skin theme that displays Related Posts in a small slider. Use this for long posts to promote more posts.\r\n\r\n[skin-related-posts heading="You may also like" qty="4"/]\r\n<h4>Did you know that Skin is AdSense ready?</h4>\r\nSkin comes with 5 pre-defined positions for a blog page (6 on single post page) where you can easily embed popular advertising services such as AdSense, AdRoll etc. Place ads in header above or below the logo, below the slider, above and inside the footer or the sidebar. Here is the scheme of the available locations.\r\n\r\n<img class="size-full wp-image-610 aligncenter" src="http://skin.nordwoodthemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/widget_areas.png" alt="" width="871" height="704" />\r\n\r\nSkin is easily customizable and flexible theme. It gives you complete control over color, fonts, header area, elements you want shown or hidden. And it comes with detailed user guide / documentation with a lot of screenshots on how to set up a there. It also comes with demo content we made.\r\nBut, if you still have a problem setting up a specific element, our support is there for you. You can reach us @nordwood.ticksy.com and we will be glad ho help.', 'The most influential underground artists of 21. century', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '215-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-05-24 17:40:39', '2018-05-24 17:40:39', '', 215, 'http://itsugestion.com/dev/testkd/215-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
